
Disease Prediction from Medical Data

Developed a predictive healthcare system that estimates the likelihood of diseases using patient medical information.

Key Features

Medical data preprocessing
Feature selection and analysis
Disease risk prediction
Models implemented:
Logistic Regression
Support Vector Machine (SVM)
Random Forest
XGBoost
Performance comparison and evaluation
Technologies Used
Python
NumPy
Pandas
Matplotlib
Seaborn
Scikit-learn
TensorFlow
Keras
OpenCV
Librosa
